<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>물품 내놓기 - MyMarket</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-light">
  <div class="container mt-5" style="max-width: 600px;">
    <div class="card p-4 shadow-sm">
      <h3 class="mb-4 text-center fw-bold">🛒 마켓에 물품 내놓기</h3>
      <form action="/product/create" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
        
        <div class="mb-3">
          <label class="form-label">물품 제목</label>
          <input type="text" name="title" class="form-control" required>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
            <label class="form-label">판매 가격</label>
            <input type="number" name="price" class="form-control" required>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
            <label class="form-label">판매 재고 수량</label>
            <input type="number" name="stock" class="form-control" value="1" min="1" required>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-3">
          <label class="form-label">기본 상세 설명</label>
          <textarea name="content" class="form-control" rows="3" placeholder="내용을 직접 적으시거나 아래 문서를 연동하세요."></textarea>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-3">
          <label class="form-label">🔗 상품 이미지 주소(URL)</label>
          <input type="text" name="imageUrl" class="form-control" placeholder="https://... 로 시작하는 이미지 주소를 입력하세요" required>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mb-4 p-3 bg-info bg-opacity-10 border rounded">
          <label class="form-label fw-bold text-info-emphasis">📄 문서 첨부 자동 반영 (.txt)</label>
          <input type="file" name="textFile" class="form-control" accept=".txt">
          <div class="form-text">선택한 텍스트 파일 내부 글귀가 자동으로 설명에 추가 삽입됩니다.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="d-grid gap-2">
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success fw-bold">물품 등록</button>
          <a href="/" class="btn btn-light border">돌아가기</a>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
